metadata.name: Australian Fot Poox
metadata.description: Australian Fot Poox will be used to acquire future exclusive works of concept and art from Mr. Regular and Mfer Prodookshons. Collecting these high-end arts will bring you closer to the potential of owning an actual Mfer Prodookshons Producer Pass. Proceeds from AFP will be used to purchase an Mfer from the official Mfers collection on the Ethereum blockchain. (contingent upon the described collection sales perimeters)
